room_title: Escape room "A Pirate's Quest" by Rockville Escape Rooms in Rockville
room_description: Three hundred years ago, pirate Captain Blye evaded pursuit just long enough to bury his treasure. But someone (or something) caught up with him before he could return to claim it. Now, armed with his treasure map, you must find the hidden booty before the ghosts of his vengeful crew arrive to claim it - and you!
